{
  "word": "decisive",
  "wordRoot": [
    {
      "title": "<span id=\"#858\" class=\"scroll-m-16 text-3xl font-bold flex items-center\"><h1 class=\"inline !mb-1 scroll-m-16 text-3xl font-bold\">decisive</h1><div class=\"pl-2 flex-1 text-textSecondary text-xl font-serif\">(adj.)</div></span>",
      "html": "<p>1610年代，“具有决定能力或力量”的意思来自中世纪拉丁语 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">decisivus</span>，源自拉丁语 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">decis-</span>， <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">decidere</span> 的过去分词词干“切断； 决定”（见 <a href=\"/cn/word/decide\" title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of decide \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\">decide</a>）。意思是“具有迅速决断的特点”始于1736年。与 <a href=\"/cn/word/decided\" title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of decided \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\">decided</a> 相似。相关词汇: <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">Decisively</span>（果断地）； <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">decisiveness</span>（决断力）。</p><ins class=\"adsbygoogle relative inline-block transition-all inline-block h-[250px] w-[300px]\" data-ad-slot=\"4000736339\" data-adtest=\"off\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"></ins>"
    }
  ],
  "relate": [
    {
      "title": "decide<div class=\"pl-2 flex-1 text-textSecondary text-xl font-serif\">(v.)</div>",
      "html": "<p>14世纪晚期，“解决争端，确定争议”，源自古法语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">decider</i>，源自拉丁语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">decidere</i>，“决定，确定”，字面意思是“切断”，来自 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">de</i> “断开”（见 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of de- \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/de-\">de-</a>）+ <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">caedere</i> “切割”（源自 PIE 词根 <a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of *kae-id- \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/*kae-id-\">*kae-id-</a> “打击”）。关于拉丁语元音变化，请参见 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of acquisition \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/acquisition\">acquisition</a>。意义是“一下子解决困难”。1830年有“下定决心”的意思。相关词汇： <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of Decided \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/decided\">Decided</a>； <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">deciding</i>。</p>"
    },
    {
      "title": "decided<div class=\"pl-2 flex-1 text-textSecondary text-xl font-serif\">(adj.)</div>",
      "html": "<p>\"坚决的，没有犹豫或动摇\"，1790年，过去分词形容词，源自 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of decide \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/decide\">decide</a>。一个 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">decided</i> 的胜利是现实毫无疑问的； 一个 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of decisive \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/decisive\">decisive</a> 的胜利则在很大程度上解决了某些问题。意思上的\"没有歧义或不确定性\"也来自于1790年。相关词汇： <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">Decidedly</i>。</p>"
    }
  ]
}